    INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [x.Size2] ON [x2].[SizeId] = [x.Size2].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [x.Color2] ON [x2].[ColorId] = [x.Color2].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [x.Product2] ON [x2].[ProductId] = [x.Product2].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [x.Product.ProductCategory2] ON [x.Product2].[CategoryId] = [x.Product.ProductCategory2].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Bills] AS [x.Bill2] ON [x2].[BillId] = [x.Bill2].[Id]
    WHERE [x2].[BillId] = @__billId_0
) AS [t2] ON [x.Product.ProductCategory.Products].[CategoryId] = [t2].[Id0]
ORDER BY [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)
